      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments conducted at flow rates 2–6 L/min and impeller speeds 2000–3500 RPM using ASTM F1841 blood analog fluid at 37°C. All conditions fall within COU operating envelope. Temperature and viscosity controlled within ±5%."
    },
