      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis and relative hemolysis index are the FDA-recognized QoIs for centrifugal blood pump hemolysis assessment. Both QoIs are directly computed from CFD shear stress fields using the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law damage model, providing a direct link to the clinical endpoint."
