    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 allowances for MRL 2 with medium model influence. Mesh independence study demonstrates GCI < 1.2%; experimental comparison yields mean relative error 8.3% against three independent laboratories. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied across all five operating points. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device and supporting the 510(k) substantial equivalence determination.",
